## Challenges in Incorporating Customer Feedback

While integrating customer feedback is beneficial, it comes with its challenges:

- **Volume of Feedback:** Managing large volumes of feedback can be overwhelming without the right systems in place.
- **Conflicting Feedback:** Customers may have conflicting opinions, making it challenging to decide which feedback to act upon.
- **Resource Limitations:** Limited resources can restrict the ability to implement all desired changes.

